statements: SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY age ASC;
SELECT gender, ethnicity FROM demographic_data WHERE income > 50000;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE zip_code LIKE '9%' AND health_condition = 'diabetes';
SELECT id, gender, income FROM demographic_data WHERE gender = 'Male' ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT age, income FROM demographic_data WHERE ethnicity = 'Caucasian'
SELECT id, age, gender, ethnicity FROM demographic_data WHERE age >= 30 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT id, gender, income FROM demographic_data WHERE ethnicity = 'Asian' ORDER BY income DESC;
SELECT * FROM demographic_data WHERE zip_code LIKE '9%' AND health_condition = 'Diabetes';
SELECT age, income, gender FROM demographic_data WHERE income > 50000 ORDER BY age ASC, income DESC;
SELECT id, ethnicity, zip_code FROM demographic_data WHERE ethnicity IN ('Black', 'Hispanic') AND age < 40 ORDER BY zip_code ASC;
SELECT * FROM DemographicData;
SELECT id, age, gender FROM DemographicData WHERE age > 30;
SELECT ethnicity, COUNT(*) FROM DemographicData GROUP BY ethnicity;
SELECT * FROM HealthInterventions WHERE intervention_budget > 1000;
SELECT intervention_id, intervention_name, target_population FROM HealthInterventions ORDER BY intervention_name DESC;
SELECT id, age, gender FROM DemographicData WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT * FROM DemographicData WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT intervention_name, intervention_budget FROM HealthInterventions ORDER BY intervention_budget ASC;
SELECT id, age, ethnicity FROM DemographicData WHERE risk_factor = 'High' ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT id, gender, ethnicity FROM DemographicData WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 40 ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT * FROM demographics;
SELECT id, age, gender FROM demographics WHERE age > 30;
SELECT condition_name, diagnosis_date FROM health_conditions ORDER BY diagnosis_date DESC;
SELECT intervention_name, target_group FROM interventions WHERE end_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, condition_name, severity FROM health_conditions WHERE severity = 'High';
SELECT * FROM demographics ORDER BY age DESC, gender ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, ethnicity FROM demographics WHERE income > 50000 AND age BETWEEN 25 AND 40;
SELECT condition_name FROM health_conditions WHERE severity = 'High' OR severity = 'Medium';
SELECT intervention_name, start_date, end_date FROM interventions WHERE target_group = 'Children' ORDER BY start_date ASC;

SELECT d.id, d.age, h.condition_name, i.intervention_name FROM demographics d JOIN health_conditions h ON d.id = h.patient_id JOIN interventions i ON h.id = i.id WHERE d.gender = 'Female' AND i.start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM high_risk_populations;
SELECT population_name, risk_level FROM high_risk_populations WHERE risk_level > 3;
SELECT intervention_name, target_group, effectiveness_score FROM health_interventions ORDER BY intervention_name ASC;
SELECT id, age, gender, ethnicity, city FROM population_demographics WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 40;
SELECT intervention_name, intervention_date, success_rate FROM intervention_tracking WHERE success_rate >= 0.8 ORDER BY success_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM high_risk_populations;
SELECT population_name, risk_level FROM high_risk_populations WHERE risk_level > 5;
SELECT intervention_name, effectiveness_score FROM health_interventions ORDER BY effectiveness_score DESC;
SELECT population_id, age, gender, ethnicity, city FROM population_demographics WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 40 AND gender = 'Male';

SELECT intervention_name, target_group, success_rate FROM health_interventions INNER JOIN intervention_tracking ON health_interventions.id = intervention_tracking.intervention_id WHERE success_rate > 0.8;
SELECT * FROM demographics;
SELECT age, gender FROM demographics WHERE income > 50000;
SELECT DISTINCT ethnicity FROM demographics;
SELECT * FROM health_conditions ORDER BY diagnosis_date DESC;
SELECT intervention_name, start_date, end_date FROM interventions WHERE target_population = 'Children';
SELECT age, gender, ethnicity FROM demographics ORDER BY age ASC;
SELECT health_status, record_date FROM patient_health WHERE health_status = 'Good';
SELECT condition, diagnosis_date FROM health_conditions WHERE (diagnosis_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31') ORDER BY diagnosis_date DESC;
SELECT intervention_name, target_population, start_date, end_date FROM interventions WHERE target_population = 'Children' ORDER BY start_date ASC;

SELECT intervention_logs.log_date, interventions.intervention_name, demographics.age FROM intervention_logs JOIN interventions ON intervention_logs.intervention_id = interventions.id JOIN demographics ON intervention_logs.patient_id = demographics.id ORDER BY log_date DESC;
